          "title": "The Mishnah's case of cascading Nezirut declarations and annulment of the first person's status",
          "display_title": "Cascading Status",
          "timestamp": "26:31"
        },
        {
          "title": "When a wife declares Nezirut and the husband responds with va'ani: the husband cannot annul his own status",
          "display_title": "Wife First",
