          "title": "Reish Lakish's position: all va'ani declarations must occur within tokh kedei dibbur of the first person's statement",
          "display_title": "Reish Lakish",
          "timestamp": "33:25"
        },
        {
          "title": "Definition and duration of tokh kedei dibbur as the measure of valid subsequent declarations",
          "display_title": "Tokh Kedei Dibbur",
          "timestamp": "37:55"
        },
        {
          "title": "Debate over whether each va'ani piggybacks on the immediately preceding person or all on the first declarant",
          "display_title": "Piggyback Chain",
